channel.title: == Your best Auxy track this year? ==
channel.description: Howdy! Along with the 2019 Auxy forum awards, the Auxy Collective has agreed to help promote a playlist full of **your** very own **best** tracks of 2019. On this thread, please post one track, you think and feel is your personal best on 2019. At the end of December, **all** tracks will be combined into a playlist. We thank you all for such an amazing year, and look forward to the upcoming years, with Auxy.
